1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Neo wasn’t the system’s mistake… he was its choice.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
The Matrix knew someone would question reality—so it prepared for him.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Every version of the simulation produced an anomaly… but Neo was different.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
His code wasn’t random—it was sculpted by the system over generations.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
The Matrix needed him… because without the One, the cycle can’t reset.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
But here’s the twist: Neo had to believe he chose rebellion on his own.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
The Oracle didn’t predict Neo—she nurtured the choices that made him unstoppable.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
The Matrix didn’t pick Neo because he would follow it… but because he would break it.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Only Neo could force the system to evolve beyond control.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
The Matrix chose Neo not as its savior… but as its evolution.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Anyway, Subscribe for more

